<item>
            <title>[FELIX-477] BND: Versions with fourth section all numbers are truncated</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-477</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If i set the pom version or the Bundle-Version directive to &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1.1.0-200801301117&lt;br/&gt;
1.1.0.200801301117&lt;br/&gt;
1.1.0-20080130&lt;br/&gt;
1.1.0.20080130&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;the version in the manifest is truncated to 1.1.0&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If version is &lt;br/&gt;
1.1.0-qualifier&lt;br/&gt;
1.1.0.qualifier&lt;br/&gt;
then it&apos;s not truncated&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
